Name: Fate of Dynasty
About the game: Fate of Dynasty is a short lore exploration puzzle game inspired by walking simulators such as Gone Home, Dear Esther, and Layers of Fear. Figure out how to perform the ritual to put an end to the tyranny of the ruling dynasty. Fate of Dynasty was developed during the Global Game Jam 2021 and is an open-source project.
